casebody.data:
James L. SNEED, Jr., petitioner,
v.
Rodney BURRISS, Judge, Circuit Court of Kentucky, Bullitt County, et al. No. 16-8047. Supreme Court of the United States April 17, 2017.

Motion of The National Association for Public Defense, et al. for leave to file a brief as amici curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of Kentucky denied.
